node.text: Y’all already know I have some expressive brows and since we’re all wearing masks now, I rely on my brows to do the across the room communicating. Which can be hard! Which is why I teamed up with @schickhydrosilk to expertly shape my brows and spoke to body language expert @blancacobb to master above the mask communication🦋 #hydrosilkbrowtalk #brandpartner
